pageContext.claim: “And a swamp creature with ‘pull’ was just sentenced to two months in jail for a similar thing that they want Stone to serve 9 years for. A phony Mueller Witch Hunt disgrace. Caught!”
pageContext.analysis: There's hardly any similarity. Trump is referring to James Wolfe, a former Senate staff member who pleaded guilty to one felony count of lying to the FBI. Stone was convicted of seven felonies including lying to Congress and witness tampering.
